replies.body:
When immobile mages aren't allowed to be viable just so mobile assassins can be stronger {{champion:101}} 

When sustain becomes less powerful instead of bullying in the bot lane just for flashier plays {{champion:16}} 

When only Alistar and Maokai can actually last 5 seconds in a teamfight out of all the tanks {{item:3035}} 

When Veigar's "compensation" does to him more harm than Zed's nerf did to him {{champion:45}} 

When HP becomes more of a stat used against you rather than in your defense {{champion:67}} 

When lore gets completely erased and replaced by big fat question marks {{champion:32}} 

When mobility is such a big advantage every top banned champion has it in some way {{champion:76}} 

When a support like Sona pays for oppressing while there are others that go full-agression all day {{champion:89}} 

When melee top laners that can't jungle get completely kicked out of the meta, and ranged, new, kiting champions are released to make them even less successful {{champion:150}} 

When AD champions get %HP magic damage to make it harder for tanks to itemize against them {{champion:429}} 

When every new champion needs to come with two more passives than the last one {{champion:157}}
